kButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_14908305\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 17, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104qws1743437795223.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qws1743437795223.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qws1743437795223.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"qws1743437795223\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">To work with Interface Version 2, each UX widget or your custom widget must include the\n\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">uxInterfaceVersion = 2</code> setting in the physical widget definition\n\t\tsection of the <span class=\"ph filepath\">web.ini</span> file. Developers must ensure this setting is\n\t\tadded when implementing a custom widget with Interface Version 2.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Note that a UX or custom widget implemented with an earlier Interface version does not contain\n\t\t\tthis setting. If a widget is missing this setting or has a value other than 2, it\n\t\t\tgenerates the following runtime error:</p>\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-263 : UWEBERR_UX_INTERFACE_VERSION_MISMATCH</code></p>\n<p class=\"p\">This error is generated for each widget with a version mismatch while loading a DSP page.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">You can resolve the Interface version mismatch in one of the following ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"qws1743437795223__ul_ksl_gtx_v2c\">\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lrs1748341244336.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lrs1748341244336.html\" title=\"UX Widget Interface Version 2 introduces a new format for the data argument in the UX Widget Interface API functions: processLayout, onConnect, dataUpdate, and dataCleanup.\">Upgrade your widget to be compatible with Interface Version 2</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yic1748341382854.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yic1748341382854.html\" title=\"To make your code compatible with the new interface version 2 with minimum effort, you can use the compatibility utility. It is located by default in the uniface/webapps/ux_compatibility_utils/v2_to_v1_ux_interface_converter.js. folder.\">Update your widget to be compatible with Interface Version 2</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_14908305\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_14908305\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Migration to Interface Version 2 Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 17, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 To work with Interface Version 2, each UX widget or your custom widget must include the uxInterfaceVersion = 2 setting in the physical widget definition section of the web.ini file. Developers must ensure this setting is added when implementing a custom widget with Interface Version 2. Note that a UX or custom widget implemented with an earlier Interface version does not contain this setting. If a widget is missing this setting or has a value other than 2, it generates the following runtime error: -263 : UWEBERR_UX_INTERFACE_VERSION_MISMATCH This error is generated for each widget with a version mismatch while loading a DSP page. You can resolve the Interface version mismatch in one of the following ways: Upgrade your widget to be compatible with Interface Version 2 Update your widget to be compatible with Interface Version 2 Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}